Third-party components
----------------------

usb-serial-for-android
  Used on Android for USB-serial chipset drivers (FTDI, CP21xx, CH34x,
  PL2303, CDC/ACM, ...). Its sources are vendored under
  third_party/usb-serial-for-android/ and compiled into an embedded
  classes.dex at build time. See that directory for its license.

boost (boost::asio)
  Used on Linux/Windows for portable serial I/O. Header-only usage; not
  redistributed.
